{
	"info": {
		"_postman_id": "bellezapp-auth-collection",
		"name": "Bellezapp POS - Autenticación",
		"description": "Colección de Postman para la autenticación en Bellezapp POS Backend - Incluye registro, login y perfil de usuario",
		"schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
	},
	"item": [
		{
			"name": "Autenticación",
			"item": [
				{
					"name": "Registrar Usuario",
					"event": [
						{
							"listen": "test",
							"script": {
								"exec": [
									"if (pm.response.code === 201) {",
									"    const jsonData = pm.response.json();",
									"    if (jsonData.token) {",
									"        pm.environment.set(\"authToken\", jsonData.token);",
									"        pm.environment.set(\"userId\", jsonData.user._id);",
									"        console.log(\"Token guardado:\", jsonData.token);",
									"    }",
									"}"
								],
								"type": "text/javascript"
							}
						}
					],
					"request": {
						"method": "POST",
						"header": [
							{
								"key": "Content-Type",
								"value": "application/json",
								"type": "text"
							}
						],
						"body": {
							"mode": "raw",
							"raw": "{\n    \"username\": \"admin\",\n    \"email\": \"admin@bellezapp.com\",\n    \"firstName\": \"Admin\",\n    \"lastName\": \"Sistema\",\n    \"password\": \"Admin123!\",\n    \"role\": \"admin\"\n}"
						},
						"url": {
							"raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/auth/register",
							"host": [
								"{{baseUrl}}"
							],
							"path": [
								"api",
								"auth",
								"register"
							]
						},
						"description": "Registra un nuevo usuario en el sistema.\n\n**Campos requeridos:**\n- `username`: Nombre de usuario único\n- `email`: Correo electrónico único\n- `firstName`: Nombre\n- `lastName`: Apellido\n- `password`: Contraseña (mínimo 6 caracteres)\n- `role`: Rol del usuario (admin, manager, cashier)\n\n**Respuesta exitosa (201):**\n```json\n{\n    \"message\": \"User registered successfully\",\n    \"token\": \"jwt_token_here\",\n    \"user\": {\n        \"_id\": \"user_id\",\n        \"username\": \"admin\",\n        \"email\": \"admin@bellezapp.com\",\n        \"firstName\": \"Admin\",\n        \"lastName\": \"Sistema\",\n        \"role\": \"admin\",\n        \"isActive\": true\n    }\n}\n```"
					},
					"response": []
				},
				{
					"name": "Registrar Cajero",
					"event": [
						{
							"listen": "test",
							"script": {
								"exec": [
									"if (pm.response.code === 201) {",
									"    const jsonData = pm.response.json();",
									"    if (jsonData.token) {",
									"        pm.environment.set(\"cashierToken\", jsonData.token);",
									"        pm.environment.set(\"cashierId\", jsonData.user._id);",
									"        console.log(\"Token de cajero guardado:\", jsonData.token);",
									"    }",
									"}"
								],
								"type": "text/javascript"
							}
						}
					],
					"request": {
						"method": "POST",
						"header": [
							{
								"key": "Content-Type",
								"value": "application/json"
							}
						],
						"body": {
							"mode": "raw",
							"raw": "{\n    \"username\": \"cajero1\",\n    \"email\": \"cajero1@bellezapp.com\",\n    \"firstName\": \"María\",\n    \"lastName\": \"González\",\n    \"password\": \"Cajero123!\",\n    \"role\": \"cashier\"\n}"
						},
						"url": {
							"raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/auth/register",
							"host": [
								"{{baseUrl}}"
							],
							"path": [
								"api",
								"auth",
								"register"
							]
						},
						"description": "Ejemplo de registro de un usuario con rol de cajero."
					},
					"response": []
				},
				{
